{"tid":1223782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有唔同意見好事嚟 但語氣唔好重 槍口對外","createTime":"2019-06-14T19:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T06:34:38.000Z","uid":71197,"like":116,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e7904e7f7978b6e175ca97f347ff9634592f6cbe","tid":1223782,"uid":71197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:34:41.000Z","msg":"留意到唔少post入面意見有分歧嘅時候，會有啲ching難免情緒主導咗少少，好急切想話俾樓主/其他巴絲聽佢地嘅意見入面有啲咩缺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 語氣可能會重咗少少，搞到大家唔和氣，咁樣唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上大家都係想件事好，想成功撤回而有唔同嘅諗法，互相提出意見好事嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但有時可以注意語氣，避免內部爭執，打擊士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，6月16一齊出嚟遊行反送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb8d154bb0f8a2a2b2b47e6905de393d9dc50dc3","tid":1223782,"uid":71197,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:40:23.000Z","msg":"雖然屌嚟屌去都算係連登文化嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但特別喺呢個情況下盡量試下對自己友放寬下態度好啲"},{"pid":"65dfe3a2182d37f8f9fd57b0236acbf1fa342451","tid":1223782,"uid":2419,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:43:21.000Z","msg":"大家都好繃緊<br />\n<br />\n諗一諗先好留言"},{"pid":"c72d1e1d2c8ae9f80fcea5e2bae57ddd4b1a4e12","tid":1223782,"uid":71197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"65dfe3a2182d37f8f9fd57b0236acbf1fa342451","tid":1223782,"uid":2419,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:43:21.000Z","msg":"大家都好繃緊<br />\n<br />\n諗一諗先好留言"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:47:59.000Z","msg":"都相信呢到每位巴絲都係長期好緊張嘅狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗自己為咗大家著想 諗一諗先再回應啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5d48c7